# Helios Flutter

Read **`AGENTS.md`** at the repo root for architecture, env vars, and plugin rules.

- **Plugins never own Google Sign-In**; only the host shows the **single Google login** screen.
- Identity tokens for APIs: **Helios JWT from Helios Core** after Google ID token exchange — not the Google access token.
- Feature packages depend on **`helios_auth_contract`** only; the host implements `HeliosAuth` and injects it into plugin UIs/routes.
